    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "description": "LIVE. Real Claude spend rate ($/h) summed across all projects, derived from the durable operator_task_tokens_total{model,type} series priced per-model (same formula as task-delivery.json 'Cost (USD) by Kind and Repo': opus-4-8 $5/$25 per 1M in/out, sonnet-5 $3/$15, haiku-4-5 $1/$5; cache_read 0.1x input, cache_creation 1.25x input). Repointed off the never-emitted claude_code_cost_usage_total OTel guess (no OTLP->Prometheus collector wired; zero series) and off the dead ccw_turn_cost_usd_total (result.json is never written). Once CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TELEMETRY + the OTLP->Prometheus collector land, Claude Code's native claude_code.cost.usage becomes the authoritative cross-check; confirm the collector's scraped name then (add_metric_suffixes appends a unit token, e.g. claude_code_cost_usage_usd_total).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "none"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]
          },
          "unit": "currencyUSD"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22},
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum( rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"input\", model=\"claude-opus-4-8\"}[1h]) * 5e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"output\", model=\"claude-opus-4-8\"}[1h]) * 25e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"cache_read\", model=\"claude-opus-4-8\"}[1h]) * 0.5e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"cache_creation\", model=\"claude-opus-4-8\"}[1h]) * 6.25e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"input\", model=\"claude-sonnet-5\"}[1h]) * 3e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"output\", model=\"claude-sonnet-5\"}[1h]) * 15e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"cache_read\", model=\"claude-sonnet-5\"}[1h]) * 0.3e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"cache_creation\", model=\"claude-sonnet-5\"}[1h]) * 3.75e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"input\", model=\"claude-haiku-4-5\"}[1h]) * 1e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"output\", model=\"claude-haiku-4-5\"}[1h]) * 5e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"cache_read\", model=\"claude-haiku-4-5\"}[1h]) * 0.1e-6 or rate(operator_task_tokens_total{type=\"cache_creation\", model=\"claude-haiku-4-5\"}[1h]) * 1.25e-6 ) * 3600",
          "legendFormat": "cost $/h",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Real Cost Rate ($/h, priced operator_task_tokens_total)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "efihqbqlmroqod"},
      "description": "Reactive 429 backstop: the always-on floor of the degradation ladder. Count per 5m of agent-pod log lines indicating a Claude API 429 / rate-limit, sourced from Loki (count_over_time on {namespace=\"tatara\", app=\"tatara-claude-code-wrapper\"}), NOT a Prometheus counter: Claude Code's claude_code.api_error is an OTel LOG EVENT, so a claude_code_api_error_total metric will never exist even after the OTLP collector lands. Reads 0 until agents surface Anthropic 429s in their logs (e.g. once CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TELEMETRY log export or wrapper 429-logging lands). A sustained non-zero count means agents are hitting the account rate limit despite the proactive gate. Follow-up: once the exact log schema is known, tighten the line filter to a json field per CONVENTIONS.md / tatara-logs.yaml (confirm the status key: status vs status_code vs http.status_code).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": {"legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false},
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": {"type": "linear"},
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": {"group": "A", "mode": "none"},
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "off"}
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22},
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "legend": {"calcs": ["mean", "lastNotNull"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi", "sort": "desc"}
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {"type": "loki", "uid": "efihqbqlmroqod"},
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"tatara\", app=\"tatara-claude-code-wrapper\"} |~ `(?i)(429|rate.?limit)` [5m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "429s /5m",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "API 429 Rate-Limit Hits (agent-pod logs, /5m)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
